218928", "2013218926", "2330-5975", "2013218925"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Bismarck daily tribune", "Bismarck evening tribune"], "partof": ["the bismarck tribune (bismarck, north dakota) 1916-current [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 51.850834, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["burleigh", "newspapers", "morton", "north dakota", "mandan", "bismarck (n.d.)", "periodicals", "electronic journals", "united states", "bismarck"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:48:24.858Z", "title": "The Bismarck tribune", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2013218926/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2013218927/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1878", "dates": ["[1878 TO 1884]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with vol. VI, no. 19 (October 9, 1878); ceased with vol. XI, no. 52 (May 30, 1884). Daily ed.: Bismarck daily tribune, 1881-1884. Triweekly ed.: Bismarck tri-weekly tribune, 1878-1881. Description based on: Vol. VI, no. 19 (October 9, 1878); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 21, 2013). Latest issue consulted: Vol. XI, no. 52 (May 30, 1884) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 21, 2013). Bismarck weekly tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1884 : Online) 2330-605X (DLC) 2013218928 (OCoLC)856527496"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:22.594Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2013218927/", "image_url": [], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["north dakota", "burleigh", "united states", "bismarck"], "number": ["2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2013218924", "2330-6017", "856524485", "2013218923", "2013218927", "online resource", "2013218928", "2013218925"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Bismarck weekly tribun